article_id:935,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, Dragonyule Defenders 2, Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A new summon showcase, Dragonyule Defenders 2, went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576130400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This summon showcase features limited-time adventurers and a new dragon!<br>It also features the limited-time adventurers and limited-time dragon from the previous &quot;Dragonyule Defenders&quot; summon showcase.<br>In addition, all of the featured adventurers and dragons have boosted appearance rates!<br><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>Note: The newly added 5★ dragon Corsaint Phoenix will also be part of the summoning pool in all upcoming summon showcases.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured limited-time adventurers:</div><div>5★ Dragonyule Malora (light/axe)</div><div>4★ Dragonyule Xainfried (wind/wand)</div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured dragons:</div><div>5★ Corsaint Phoenix (light)</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragons reappearing for a limited time:</div><div><br></div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Dragonyule Cleo (water/dagger)</div><div>4★ Dragonyule Nefaria (water/bow)</div><div>4★ Dragonyule Xander (water/wand)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Dragonyule Jeanne d&#39;Arc (water)</div><div><br></div><div>Note: Non-limited dragons are also featured.</div><div>For information about other featured adventurers and dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576130400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577339940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured dragons and limited-time featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div><div class="summ